== 物理性質 ==
目前瞭解到的關於小行星719的情況，大多來自於在它被重新發現後的採取的觀察。2001年，它從[[地球|地球]]附近掠過，使得[[天文學家|天文學家]]得以在一系列不同的[[相角|相角]]開展觀察。在此期間，經過計算其[[自轉|自轉]][[週期|週期]]為5.802小時，測得[[絕對星等|絕對星等]]為15.43，加上[[反照率|反照率]]為0.15的假設，得出其[[直徑|直徑]]是2.8公里<ref name=CCD-2001>{{Cite journal | title = CCD Photometry of Near-Earth Asteroids in 2001 | last = Krugly | first = Yu. N. | coauthors = Belskaya, I. N.; Chiorny, V. G.; Shevchenko, V. G.; Gaftonyuk, N. M. | journal = Proceedings of Asteroids, Comets, Meteors | volume = 500 | pages = 903–906 | bibcode = 2002ESASP.500..903K | isbn = 92-9092-810-7|date=November 2002}}</ref>。而由[[理查德·P·賓澤爾|理查德·P·賓澤爾]]領導的另外一個小組測得的絕對星等為 15.8。他們使用反照率為0.15的假設，導出的計算結果是直徑為2.4公里<ref name=NEO-properties>{{Cite journal | title = Physical Properties of Near-Earth Objects | last = Binzel | first = R. P. | coauthors = et al. | year = 2002 | publisher = [[亞利桑那大學出版社|亞利桑那大學出版社]] | journal = Asteroids III | pages = 255–271 | url = http://www.lpi.usra.edu/books/AsteroidsIII/pdf/3048.pdf | format = PDF | isbn = 0816522812 | access-date = 2011-07-24 | archive-date = 2017-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170812022733/http://www.lpi.usra.edu/books/AsteroidsIII/pdf/3048.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2001年10月，理查德·P·賓澤爾等人在5米[[海爾望遠鏡|海爾望遠鏡]]對其進行了觀測，并把它歸類為[[S-型小行星|S-型小行星]]<ref name=observed-properties>{{Cite journal | title = Observed spectral properties of near-Earth objects: results for population distribution, source regions, and space weathering processes | last = Binzel | first = R. P. | coauthors = et al. | journal = [[伊卡洛斯_(期刊)|伊卡洛斯 (期刊)]] | volume = 170 | issue = 2 | pages = 259–294 | url = http://www.mtholyoke.edu/courses/tburbine/tomburbine/binzel.2004.pdf | format = PDF | doi = 10.1016/j.icarus.2004.04.004 | bibcode = 2004Icar..170..259B | date = August 2004 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5glwslK30?url=http://www.mtholyoke.edu/courses/tburbine/tomburbine/binzel.2004.pdf | archivedate = 2009-05-14 }}</ref>。

